<item>
            <title>[LU-4446] sanityn test_51c sets fail loc on the wrong node and wouldn&apos;t work anyway</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4446</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanityn test_51c fails 100% of the time when I run it on a local setup. It sets an MDT-side fail loc (OBD_FAIL_MDS_LL_BLOCK) on the local node. It also assumes that mdt_getattr_name_lock() will wait for the layout lock, which it won&apos;t. I think the test should be deleted.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
